- Taking screenshot of the visible area of the page using Selenium
- Taking screenshot of only a UI Web element on the page using Selenium
- Taking screenshot of a section of the page using Selenium
- Taking screenshot of the Full Page using Selenium in Firefox browser
- Copying the screenshots to the desired location using FileUtils, ImageIO and FileHandler
- FileUtils from Apache Commons io
- FileHandler from Selenium
- Robot class in Java for taking screenshot with URLs and screenshots of displayed Alerts on the page
- AShot API for taking full page screenshots in all browsers
- And many more.